		<hr size="1">I have a policy: I sow, bind, buff for free...I teleport guildmembers and friends for free...and I teleport anyone else for 20pp unless a) i'm already headed that way or b) some little lvl 4 character offers everything they own for a teleport (in which case they get a free ride).  On the other hand, i don't go shouting in the zone that i will teleport for 20pp a pop; instead, whenever i see someone auctioning WTB a teleport or looking for a teleport i'll givem a tell that i'll do it for 20pp.  90% of the time people are very willing to pay this price.<P>P.S. I'm about half a bub into lvl 29 and i have already made over 300plat by teleporting.<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
