		<hr size="1">I never charge, but I do accept donations.  That goes for anything I can do.  It's only mana after all.  I can't port others yet, but I don't think my attitude will change.  I enjoy helping others.<P>The only thing that bothers me is when someone asks in a rude way.  I have gotten more than one, "Need SoW" request.  I usually ignore them till they take the time to ask politely.<P>However, you must remember that we are playing with many individuals that don't speak English well.  A few of people that I ignored turned out to be very nice non-english speaking players.<P>Faeyd<BR>22nd Level Druid<BR>Bristlebane<BR><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
