		<hr size="1">I'm so far from TP I probably have no right posting on this one. I just got SOW and I must say it's a blessing and curse at same time. I can't go 100 yards without someone asking me for SOW. <P>Which brings me to TP. I couldn't imagine how that gets. I'm all for charging to TP since Wizards do it all the time. ALL the time. Taking time out of your game should be compensated with something. <P>Also Norrath exists on an economy. It's like the cycle of life. I charge for TP. Save for split paw tunic. Sell or give my leather tunic to newbie for good price or free. Newbie uses to advance himself. He repeats after he's saved for his upgrade to armor, spells, food, etc... <P>Just an observation and opinion. <br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
