		<a href="MB_Editmsg.asp?FID=62&FN=Druid&SID=7&SN=EverQuest&TID=418266&TN=Charging+for+tp+%21%21%21%21&CAT=Classes&SURL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Eeverlore%2Ecom&MSID=418275&PL=4&amp;action=REPLY"><img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/btn_reply.gif" border="0" align="right" alt="Reply to message"></a>
